name: HeadlineNewsFromStarNewsGroup
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: Now you can get local news headlines right on your Echo or Dot device, courtesy of Star News Group of Manasquan, NJ. Stay uo to date on what's happening in your town as part of your daily Flash Briefing, and make sure to pick up The Coast Star every Thursday, The Ocean Star every Friday, or to visit us at starnewsgroup.com.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
